<div class="contribution-cta">
    <div class="cta-header">// SYSTEM_ALERT: OPEN_FOR_CONTRIBUTIONS</div>
    <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>Skeletons in the code closet?</h3>
        <p>
            Do you have a pattern from hell or a radar blip that wants to watch
            the world burn?
        </p>
        <p>Bring it on! Submit a PR on GitHub and let's suffer together.</p>

        <a
            href="https://github.com/vanto/worstofbreed.net/tree/main/src/content"
            class="cta-button"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
            [ CONTRIBUTE NOW -> ]
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .contribution-cta {
        margin-top: 5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border: var(--border-thick, 4px solid #111);
        background: var(--paper, #fff);
        box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--shadow, #666);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-header {
        background: var(--ink, #111);
        color: var(--paper, #fff);
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        font-family: var(--font-mono, "Courier New", monospace);
        border-bottom: var(--border-thick, 4px solid #111);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .cta-content {
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-content h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-content p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        background: var(--accent, #ff00ff);
        color: #000;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: var(--font-mono, "Courier New", monospace);
        font-weight: bold;
        border: var(--border-thick, 4px solid #111);
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000;
        transition:
            transform 0.1s,
            box-shadow 0.1s;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translate(2px, 2px);
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;
    }

    .cta-button:active {
        transform: translate(4px, 4px);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 #000;
    }
</style>
